ad.title: Housekeeping Manangement in the household
ad.content:
Good Day!

Dear Madam/Sir:

I would like to apply as a House Keeper in your end. I graduated from a Housekeeping NCII in my country, the Philippines. I already completed the On the Job Training of the Housekeeping Program. I believe my healthcare certifications and considerable experience make me the ideal candidate for this position.

My duties include helping with daily living and hygiene, as well as entertainment activities. Also, I'm adept at noticing subtle physical and emotional changes in patient care. 

I've attached my resume for your review and would welcome the opportunity to discuss my skills and qualifications further at the interview. 

Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to hearing from you.

Sincerely yours,


ROSELLER C. MARTINEZ JR.
